Prednisolone was granted FDA approval on 21 June 1955.[L9431]', '["D07AA03", "S01CA02", "D07XA02", "A01AC54", "R01AD02", "S01BB02", "R01AD52", "S01CB02", "V03AB05", "S03BA02", "D07BA01", "D07CA03", "S01BA04", "S02BA03", "A07EA01", "H02AB06", "S02CA01", "C05AA04", "S03CA02"]', '[]');
